Privacy Policy
Effective Date: April 6, 2025

Thank you for using AI WASHER TECH. Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your information.

1. Information We Collect
We collect the following information:
	•	Personal Data: Name and email address
	•	Non-Personal Data: Usage data such as how the app is used

2. Purpose of Data Collection
We collect this information to improve the performance, features, and user experience of AI WASHER TECH.

3. Data Sharing and Processing
	•	We send user requests to OpenAI’s API to process and generate responses.
	•	We do not store or save chat messages.
	•	We use cloud storage services such as Firebase to store user profile information.
	•	We do not sell or rent your personal data to third parties.

4. Children’s Privacy
We do not knowingly collect any personal information from children under the age of 13. If you believe a child has provided us with personal information, please contact us immediately.

5. Changes to This Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy at any time. We will post the revised policy and update the effective date. Continued use of the app means you accept the new policy.

6. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns, please contact us at: Jayappliancerepairs@gmail.com

Thank you for trusting AI WASHER TECH.
